The services   required, but not limited to, are set out as follows:
1.   Assist teachers in the cleaning of kitchens and kitchen utensils.
2. Assist   teachers in the preparation of ingredients/kitchen equipment for students’   cooking lessons/workshops during curriculum hours/within stipulated working   hours.
3. Maintain   the general cleanliness of the kitchen equipment and the workplace.
4. Ensure   proper stock-taking of all perishable ingredients and equipment (Ensure   countability of sharp equipment/s).
5.   Any other duties assigned by the Authority.


*****Previous experience of at least 1 year in performing similar functions in a school is an advantage****